1.0.name: wordpress/advanced-youtube-widget
1.0.description: A widget that will enable visitors to add youtube account or return search results, with a custom number of maximum results per account/search. It's easy to use , flexible, enables customization of picture sizes and has multiple displays by two(so far) types of content. More will be added in future versions..<br/> <br/><br/> DONATE! <br/>DONATE HERE - (any ammount using paypal or credit card) <br/>
